node_modules/
**/node_modules/

dist/
**/dist/

dist-ssr/
**/dist-ssr/

.vite/
**/.vite/

coverage/
**/coverage/

npm-debug.log*
yarn-debug.log*
yarn-error.log*
pnpm-debug.log*

